Package: Aerith
Title: Post-processing of stable isotope probing (SIP) proteomics data from Sipros output 
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Yi", "Xiong", email = "yixiong@ou.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Visualisation of peptide isotopic peaks and SIP peptide spectra match (PSM). Filtration of high quality PSM. Accurate isotopic abundance calculation of protein and peptide. Visualisation of SIP proteomics results.
